{
  "message": "\ud83c\udfa8 Use KubeStellar hexagon logo for PWA widget icon (#526)\n\nUpdate manifest.json and index.html to use kubestellar-logo.svg\nas the primary icon for the PWA widget.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
